data.chText: 硬纸板，卡纸板（常用于制造盒子）
data.enText: stiff material like very thick paper, often used for making boxes

data.chText: 人物不真实而又缺乏深度的小说
data.enText: a novel with superficial cardboard characters

means: 卡纸板(常用于制造盒子)

value.def: Cardboard is thick, stiff paper that is used, for example, to make boxes and models.

example.ex: ...a life-size cardboard cut-out of a police officer.
example.tran: 用硬纸板剪出来的、和真人一样大小的警察
